Are you looking for alternative things to do in Lagos? A beach house experience is always a good idea. Gather a group of friends and you all can spend a day partying or camping at a beach house overlooking the ocean. These are four beach houses you can book for a nice weekend getaway with your squad. This is a six bedroom luxurious and quiet beach house overlooking the Atlantic Ocean. It is ideal for a party or getaway which means you can visit for a day or sleepover. You have access to the swimming pool, waterfront, kitchen, outdoor grill and the full staff available. You will need a boat to get to the beach house which comes with all the packages available. Kamp Ikaare is a modern self-catering resort which has a pool house and 12 en-suite bedrooms. Celebrate office retreats, bridal showers, weddings and birthday parties here. It is a hidden gem and perfect if you want to be alone or with your group. If you are adventurous, come along with your camp tents and sleep on the beach. It is only accessibble by boat and is 30 minutes from Victoria Island. <img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-764441 lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Jaybee-Beach-Camp-Photo-Jaybee-Beach-Camp-1-897x598.jpg" alt="" width="897" height="598" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Jaybee-Beach-Camp-Photo-Jaybee-Beach-Camp-1-897x598.jpg 897w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Jaybee-Beach-Camp-Photo-Jaybee-Beach-Camp-1-487x325.jpg 487w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Jaybee-Beach-Camp-Photo-Jaybee-Beach-Camp-1-320x213.jpg 320w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Jaybee-Beach-Camp-Photo-Jaybee-Beach-Camp-1-640x427.jpg 640w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Jaybee-Beach-Camp-Photo-Jaybee-Beach-Camp-1-600x400.jpg 600w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Jaybee-Beach-Camp-Photo-Jaybee-Beach-Camp-1.jpg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 897px) 100vw, 897px" /> Jaybee Beach Camp is located at Tarkwa Bay. It has affordable cute wooden cabins that overlook the ocean. It is home to the popular Tarkwa Cafe where you can enjoy delicious meals. To make your stay more interesting, you can set up a bonfire and play games. Experience paradise at La Manga, a home away from home. The villa includes a mini-golf course, volleyball court, quad bikes, Jacuzzi, swimming pool, a furnished kitchen, a grill and bar. You have a private balcony that comes with a sea view room. There is an in-house chef to prepare mouth-watering dishes and you can bring your own food. It includes boat transportation in the packages offered. It is absolutely perfect for unwinding.